            "title": "健倍苗苗全年純利升51.2%至2億元,末期息11.5仙",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　《經濟通通訊社12日專訊》健倍苗苗(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02161:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02161\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02161-HK</a>)公布,截至2025年3月31日止全年純利1.97億元,按年升51.2%,每股基本盈利24.08仙,派發末期息11.5仙。計及中期股息5.5仙,全年派息共17仙。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　期內收入7.82億元,升20.6%。(rh)</p></section><section><p class=\"\">　</p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">*有關業績的詳情,請參閱該公司之正式通告</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\"></p></section></main>",
